Class FP6InstrumentationDCK

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.anss.picker.FP6InstrumentationDCK
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FP6Instrumentation

    public class FP6InstrumentationDCK
extends java.lang.Object
implements FP6Instrumentation
    This is a sample instrumentation class DCK wrote which prints out picks in more detail and creates full time series of the characteristic function values. Many other parameters from the FP6 could be written out as well.

        nscl - The NNSSSSSCCCLL for the channel
        time - The time of the first sample of the timeseries that triggered this pick, time calculations are relative to this
        npts - Number of data points in data
        data - The data points submitted to the FP6
        rate - The data rate in Hz
        makefiles - Flag on whether the Picker has been set to make data files from internals.
